  "original_title": "Dialog Blaster: Mobile plans to suit every Sri Lankan",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dialog Blaster: Mobile plans to suit every Sri Lankan",
      "author": "Sahan Weerasooriya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Today, our lives revolve around our phones, and devices. Constant communication and connectedness have become inseparable from daily life. So, whether you can\u2019t stop calling, don\u2019t stop texting, are always engaging with your online social networks, streaming videos or pursuing the love of your life, Dialog Blaster plans to provide the widest range of mobile plans in Sri Lanka, and cater to all Sri Lankans.",
        "With plans starting from as low as just Rs. 7 a day and there is a plan for everyone, whether you\u2019re looking for daily, weekly or monthly plans. Each plan comes with its own combo of services and you have the freedom to choose any number of plans to best suit your lifestyle and your needs, from Sri Lanka\u2019s widest range of mobile plans, courtesy of the nation\u2019s No.1 network.",
        "The range of plans provides you with a bundle of voice, data and SMS to give you the best value for everyday use; these plans include the Triple Blaster, Fun Blaster, Video Blaster, Data blaster, Couple Blaster, and Daily Blaster Plans.",
        "Fun Blaster & Data Blaster plans are for all your fun online social activities on Facebook, WhatsApp and Instagram, and Video Blaster Plans are for all those who love streaming YouTube. Whatever your style, you can have it your way with Dialog Blaster plans.",
        "Whether you\u2019re a casual user or a power user, you\u2019ll find the best everyday value amongst Dialog\u2019s Triple Blaster plans, including the Triple Blaster 345/- Plan, the Triple Blaster 498/- plan, and the Triple Blaster 577/- plan. These plans provide a flexible and convenient combination of data, calls and SMS.",
        "CSE slips in mid-morning trade ahead of interim budget presentation",
        "Ceylinco Life invests in a substantial stake in Kings Hospital",
        "Dialog\u2019s Govi Mithuru partners TRI to extend advisory services on tea cultivation",
        "Manudam Mehewara Initiative by Dialog, MAS, Hemas & CBL reach 10,000 families, invites all corporates to Join its countrywide emergency relief mission",
        "Leave a Reply Cancel replyYour email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *Comment Name *",
        "Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment."
      ],
